|Жанры = [[ню-метал]]<ref name=Global/><ref name="PopMatters">{{cite web|last=Langhoff |first=Josh |url=http://www.popmatters.com/pm/review/144574-limp-bizkit-gold-cobra/ |title=Limp Bizkit: Gold Cobra < PopMatters |publisher=[[PopMatters]]  |lang = en|accessdate=September 12, 2011}}</ref><br />[[рэп-метал]]<ref name="AllMus"/><br />[[фанк-метал]]<ref name="AllMus">{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/limp-bizkit-p213327|title=Limp Bizkit/AllMusic|publisher=allmusic.com|accessdate=2012-1-28|lang=en|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/65JRo17Iz|archivedate=2012-02-09}}</ref><br />[[рэп-рок]]<ref name="Sanneh">{{cite news |first=Kelefa |last=Sanneh |title=''Rappers Who Definitely Know How to Rock'' |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9B0DE2DB143DF930A35751C1A9669C8B63 |publisher=[[The New York Times]]|lang = en|date=3 December 2000 |accessdate=31 December 2008 }}</ref><ref name="Newsweek">{{cite news |title=''Long Live Rock n' Rap: Rock isn't dead, it's just moving to a hip-hop beat. So are its mostly white fans, who face questions about racial identity as old as Elvis'' |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-55145760.html |publisher=[[Newsweek]]|lang = en|date=19 July 1999 |accessdate=31 December 2008 }}</ref>
